data.text:
Sailed the 8 night Odyssey on 30Mar.

On the last night there was an adult comedy show in the main theater at 10pm. My husband and I got a kick out of the comedian and would like to see if he has anything online or if he does shows on land. Only problem ... we cannot remember his name! ü§¶‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è

Before you say, contact RCCL, we already did. Emailed the night we arrived home. Finally heard back today, only to be told they cannot give out names of employees. üôÑ

So, anyone on that cruise know the comedian's name who performed on the last night?

If not on that cruise, you still may have had him on one of your RCCL cruises before. Gentleman in his mid 60's, he opened up for a quite a few rock and roll acts back in the day. He talks about marriage (married twice), getting older, and family. I know he really likes RCCL, he spoke highly of them.

For the life of us we tried Google and YouTube and have come up empty. Never hurts to try and see if someone may know who this mystery comedian is.

You said instead of calling, which I o yes that address.

However, more importantly, the eye roll wasn't for you, it was for RCCL. My apologies if you misinterpreted that. (In my original post I gave the eye roll to them ... that was the hence part. Looking back, it didn't read that way and looked directed at you which was never my intention. I am sorry about that.)

I am just dumbfounded they couldn't give out his name when it was easily accessible before. RCCL absolutely deserves my eye roll. üòâ
